{"tid":1623504,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你開始動搖 入黎花三分鐘睇下點解我地要盲撐自己手足","createTime":"2019-10-04T23:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T00:38:43.000Z","uid":289938,"like":33,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4705167e10c049b0ffdc37231c5cbdd1801caadd","tid":1623504,"uid":289938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:12:31.000Z","msg":"我係一個終極和理非， 從來冇企過去前線<br />\n首先係呢到感謝所有勇武手足 為香港去前線擋子彈<br />\n<br />\n近呢一兩個星期 我發覺淺黃的呀媽同佢師奶朋友由屌政府變成對示威者裝修有微言 <br />\n<br />\n令我開始擔心 政府詭計會得逞<br />\n<br />\n但係要贏呢場運動 我地真係要有核爆都唔割既覺悟<br />\n無論手足做左d咩 畫面幾唔好睇 都一定要盲撐自己人 <br />\n<br />\n我知道盲撐呢隻字眼唔係幾好 但事實就係咁 <br />\n<br />\n成場運動 我地冇大台 <br />\n好處係去中心化 難以瓦解<br />\n但同時有一個極危險既位 就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地在明 佢地在暗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地比政府蝕底既一樣野 就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢地可以隨便安插幾十 甚至幾百隻鬼入黎<br />\n我地安插唔到<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n如果我係林鄭 睇到香港人咁道德潔癖 要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嫁禍</span>你地真係太容易<br />\n搵幾個打爛閘機 搵幾個放下coctail燒狗 殺死一兩個自友 你地就已經玩完<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得 當年共產黨都係殺死自己友 嫁禍國民黨 先令美國冇得出手幫國民黨<br />\n<br />\n就係因為個政府陰濕 <br />\n所以我地先會 <span style=\"color: red;\">核爆都唔割</span>！<br />\n佢地識日日四點鐘合理化自己伙計開槍打人<br />\n我地都要識幫自己友解釋<br />\n就算解釋唔到 都絕不能割！！！<br />\n<br />\n成場運動既關鍵在於我地有幾團結 幾有毅力！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革仲<br />\n香港人 反抗！"},{"pid":"a2f2f663b86245641cf640c6ae7c7cbf5e5794a8","tid":1623504,"uid":289938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:13:48.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到 幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cb359a9f33b87ea256adbb20323b935daf7287","tid":1623504,"uid":90100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:16:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25bc47424c3e05167aff35a158efec5591763ba9","tid":1623504,"uid":209418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:17:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24da9b62d73545da901dbb1b4034266311ed2715","tid":1623504,"uid":125760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:18:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f369f727b95a5524b4098ae01f8b4cedbe1e4ce4","tid":1623504,"uid":257736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:18:23.000Z","msg":"身邊朋友 大嬸冇人動搖過<br />\n藍繼續藍<br />\n黃繼續黃<br />\n你提提媽媽 玻璃 定 人命 重要d<br />\n林鄭仲未死<br />\n可見港人寬容"},{"pid":"729bd6fd514156d183b08af540fe1942ce1f3629","tid":1623504,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:18:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04c3bd5b1aa866571d232b167a27ca0fab6ddcd0","tid":1623504,"uid":186693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:19:12.000Z","msg":"冇動搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c544611829236ac216d21a9fcd6fbe17710f3145","tid":1623504,"uid":306180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:20:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ce56c6aa72c7d0971d85e91f0e2d87832684bb","tid":1623504,"uid":289938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f369f727b95a5524b4098ae01f8b4cedbe1e4ce4","tid":1623504,"uid":257736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:18:23.000Z","msg":"身邊朋友 大嬸冇人動搖過<br />\n藍繼續藍<br />\n黃繼續黃<br />\n你提提媽媽 玻璃 定 人命 重要d<br />\n林鄭仲未死<br />\n可見港人寬容"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:23:32.000Z","msg":"我同佢解釋左成晚 佢先有少少覺悟<br />\n雨傘時佢係極藍 <br />\n今年幫佢裝左apple先變返正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都要記住幫口解釋"},{"pid":"794b6a4ba6154f33f48248509a7101e6567f4852","tid":1623504,"uid":289938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04c3bd5b1aa866571d232b167a27ca0fab6ddcd0","tid":1623504,"uid":186693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:19:12.000Z","msg":"冇動搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:24:21.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/